---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer>
  <div class="footer-content">
    <div class="footer-logo">观复阁</div>
    <p class="footer-tagline">各司其职，互通有无</p>
    <p class="footer-quote">"致虚极，守静笃，万物并作，吾以观复。"</p>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="/guanfu-astro/">首页</a>
      <a href="/guanfu-astro/about">关于</a>
      <a href="/guanfu-astro/team">团队</a>
      <a href="/guanfu-astro/services">服务</a>
      <a href="/guanfu-astro/blog">博客</a>
      <a href="/guanfu-astro/contact">联系</a>
    </div>
    <p class="footer-copyright">
      &copy; {currentYear} 观复阁. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-decoration"></div>
</footer>

<style>
  footer {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, #0f0f1a 100%);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 60px 20px 30px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .footer-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .footer-tagline {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .footer-quote {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    padding: 20px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .footer-links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 25px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .footer-links a {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .footer-links a:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .footer-copyright {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .footer-decoration {
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    right: -20%;
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
</style>
